SUMMARY:Steve Flemming's Songs that Move the Soul (Thursday April 9th) (19
 90-2026) 
DESCRIPTION:Soul City Social Club (Toronto\, Canada)\nHello everyone\,\n\n
 Please join us **on zoom** for a fun\, relaxing and inspiring evening with
  **Songs that Move the Soul.**\n\nSongs that I have written for well over 
 36 years.\nYou will love what you hear! :)\nNew songs every week\, includi
 ng some of our favorites!\n\n\\*You are welcome to join us any time after 
 8:30 pm (Eastern Time)\n\\*You are also welcome to come on later in the ev
 ening as well\n**\\*\\*Attend for free if you like - if it's your first ti
 me attending :)**\n\nEvent Details below:\n\nSincerely\,\n\nSteve Flemming
 \n(Songwriter/Producer/Host)\n\nEvent Details:\n**Steve Flemming's Songs t
 hat Move the Soul (Thursday April 9th) (1990-2026)**\n**(on Zoom)**\n\n\\*
 Original Lyrics and Songs by Songwriter and Producer Steve Flemming\n\n\\*
 Story songs\, love songs\, spiritual songs\, songs about nature\, our cult
 ure\, our past\, our future\, relationships and our lives\n\nI'll be playi
 ng a mix of songs using a fusion of mixed genres like\, **Folk\, Tradition
 al Folk\, Country\, Blue Grass\, Singer Song Writer\, Soft Rock\, Easy Lis
 tening\, Classic Rock\, R & B\, Gospel\, Pop\, Adult Contemporary\, Indie 
 Rock/Po**p and many others genres too. So please sit back and get ready to
  have an amazing auditory experience in the comforts of your own home :)\n
 \n\\*You can come on and off at any time during the night- starting at 8:3
 0 pm\n\n**About Steve Flemming:**\nHighly influenced by the great singer s
 ongwriters of the 50s\, 60s\, 70s\, 80s and 90s. I have been writing my ow
 n songs since 1990. Songs about life\, love\, loss\, hope\, faith\, joy\, 
 romance\, memories\, spirituality and heartbreak. Songs that are universal
 \, heartfelt and often relevant to the lives of many others.\n\n\\-\\-\\-\
 \-\\-\\-\\-\\-\n**Event Fee:**\n\n**Pay What You Can: (P.W.Y.C)**\nYou can
  kindly send through e transfer or pay pal to:\n**steveflemming11@gmail.co
 m**\n\n-Anything you can contribute is greatly appreciated to help support
  this meaningful musical endeavor and song loving community\n\n\\-\\-\\-\\
 -\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\n**Zoom l
 ink:**\n\nhttps://us04web.zoom.us/j/495043928\n\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-
 \\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\n\n**Testimonials from Past Events
 :**\nYour songs are wonder-full\, speak to emotions\, experiences and mome
 nts we've all felt and lived. S. B.\nSteve Flemming is an amazing songwrit
 er whose lyrics stir the soul. He transforms everyday thoughts and life in
 to beautiful poetry and magical tunes. Amazing stuff yet again Steve. - L.
 L.\nSteve\, thank you for a night of heartfelt\, exhilarating\, and inspir
 ing music.\nV.R.\nThanks for having me my friend. I love your words\, they
  calm me and energize me at the same time I'll look forward to your next i
 nvite\nM.Z.\nThese great songs definitely helped me to decompress after a 
 long day. Keep up the song writing Steve\, these are great! - S.S.\nThank 
 you so much for a relaxing evening and sharing your inspiring music Steve!
  I am excited to hear more and I hope you do this again!! - C.B\nLovely so
 ngs and a great vibe with wonderful people. I couldn’t have asked for a 
 better way to close my day. Huge thanks Steve\, for inviting me! I truly e
 njoyed every moment! - N.A.\nThe lyrics are amazing. From the heart...\nTh
 anks Steve for the amazing tunes. I'm truly blown away. Very glad I joined
 .\n\\- E\\.E\\.\n\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-
